query:
INSERT INTO preferences (
                user_uuid,
                use_default_accent_color,
                accent_color,
                show_separator,
                multi_select,
                save_on_pause,
                show_body_border
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
            ON CONFLICT (user_uuid) DO UPDATE
                SET use_default_accent_color = $2,
                    accent_color = $3,
                    show_separator = $4,
                    multi_select = $5,
                    save_on_pause = $6,
                    show_body_border = $7
